{"tid":1883833,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【LIVE】衞生署及醫管局4點半疫情簡報會","createTime":"2020-02-17T08:28:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T10:03:47.000Z","uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"3d0229077f1142e2b2d33b3cb311147f29dd882d","tid":1883833,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T08:28:53.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎肆虐中國內地，而本港昨日（16日）再多1宗確診，累積個案增至57宗，當中更有確診患者曾到訪醫管局總部大樓，並與相關職員開會。衞生署及醫管局今午4時半再就新型冠狀病毒感染個案的最新情況舉行簡報會，衞生署衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君醫生和醫院管理局總行政經理（質素及標準）劉家獻醫生將會出席。《蘋果》屆時將適時直播。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200217/W4DNJM4SJUCRNBFPTBIIXQSTXQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200217%2FW4DNJM4SJUCRNBFPTBIIXQSTXQ%2F&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ1lsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=65ba1c15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200217%2FW4DNJM4SJUCRNBFPTBIIXQSTXQ%2F&h=d15f46f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200217/W4DNJM4SJUCRNBFPTBIIXQSTXQ/</a>"},{"pid":"8111ee0c397fae5d240ff73544cfb80372b847d0","tid":1883833,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T08:29:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hVkmdRNl__k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhVkmdRNl__k&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ1lsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=8d1b1f42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hVkmdRNl__k</a>"},{"pid":"f7b7979f8a8f2d5ba91746027b7d6a944bcb8c92","tid":1883833,"uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T08:29:32.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】消息指，再多兩人初步確診新型冠狀病毒，是太古城確診者的太太及同事。<br />\n<br />\n太古城54歲確診者，他的太太亦出現病徵送院。消息指，她亦初步確診感染冠狀病毒。<br />\n<br />\n太古城確診者任職位一間跨國建築工程事務所，最後上班是本月六日。據了解，公司一名45歲男同事病毒測試亦呈陽性。公司已發信予員工，通報有職員確診，公司會暫停開放消毒，直至本月廿三日。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，兩人曾經代表公司一同到醫管局總部開會，除醫管局代表外，還包括其他工程公司代表。消息指，有與會者發燒。"},{"pid":"b124347c6752bc7faaa2642f13bcd14e01c5ca95","tid":1883833,"uid":346806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T08:30:19.000Z","msg":"究竟點野到"},{"pid":"9c15b4b1c3bd97d12943a76d959770f2f95fe617","tid":1883833,"uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T08:30:22.000Z","msg":"李家超去機場送機接疫船港人返黎，呢個記者會應該成班記者問衛生署問到口啞"},{"pid":"ccd207745ceed304eb37f82c94a1cd82ef6760c1","tid":1883833,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T08:32:50.000Z","msg":"隔離條友換咗人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d82319e66f2e4d273e8dbcc944d60b98c65d8ea","tid":1883833,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T08:33:27.000Z","msg":"#58 睇咗4次私家1次街症 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45d0bcd8243514ddfc24faa7edd4ad08c7bddaf6","tid":1883833,"uid":346806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T08:34:10.000Z","msg":"港島重災區"},{"pid":"c702844456710999247eb202639e2402ab5d683a","tid":1883833,"uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T08:34:20.000Z","msg":"#58<br />\n69歲 有長期病患<br />\n睇過幾次私家醫生<br />\n2月15睇長沙灣門診<br />\n住將軍澳<br />\n14日內冇外遊<br />\n新年可能有"},{"pid":"99af0873ed566b2f85f49b48314f3750f7cdaaec","tid":1883833,"uid":30647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c702844456710999247eb202639e2402ab5d683a","tid":1883833,"uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T08:34:20.000Z","msg":"#58<br />\n69歲 有長期病患<br />\n睇過幾次私家醫生<br />\n2月15睇長沙灣門診<br />\n住將軍澳<br />\n14日內冇外遊<br />\n新年可能有"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T08:35:07.000Z","msg":"未知源頭"},{"pid":"91507f54a4d056a39d823528b444a903e4a3088b","tid":1883833,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T08:35:25.